seo: 万户OA,SQL注入漏洞,DocumentEdit.jsp,指纹识别,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测万户OA系统中DocumentEdit.jsp文件的SQL注入漏洞，并通过特定请求包进行指纹识别和漏洞验证。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the SQL injection vulnerability in the DocumentEdit.jsp file of the Wanhu OA system, and performs fingerprint identification and vulnerability verification through specific request packets.
